TopicTitle: I made a star and exoplanet catalog!

Articles.Content:
Link here: https://sites.google.com/site/catalogofstarsandplanets/home

I added cool names to some of the exoplanets such as Bellona and Vulcania.

ALL NAMES ARE MY IDEAS (Except for the planets Bellerophon and Osiris)

What does everyone think?

Edited October 4, 2014 by _Augustus_

Disclaim where proposed names/nicknames are your own ideas - there's a chance that some of the planets you suggested names for are among the batch that the IAU will be having a (pre-curated) public vote over soon. It might confuse people into thinking that it's related.
